T*
(  src/features/            Feature engineering) Tj
T*
(  src/models/              Training, evaluation, prediction) Tj
T*
(  src/pipelines/           Declarative pipeline runner) Tj
T*
(  src/serving/             FastAPI serving layer) Tj
T*
(  src/rag/                 RAG/GenAI assistant foundation) Tj
T*
(  src/monitoring/          Drift and retraining checks) Tj
T*
(  tests/                   Unit tests) Tj
T*
(  .github/workflows/      GitHub Actions CI) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5. Tools And Frameworks) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Python) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Python is used as the main programming language because it has strong support for data) Tj
T*
(engineering, machine learning, APIs, and GenAI integrations.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(PySpark) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(PySpark is used for the scalable data-processing path. It is suitable for large datasets because) Tj
T*
(it can distribute reads, joins, aggregations, and writes across a Spark cluster.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(In this project, PySpark is used for:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- reading large CSV files) Tj
T*
