T*
(FastAPI is used to expose the trained model through an API.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Endpoints include:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- /health: service health check) Tj
T*
(- /predict: reorder prediction) Tj
T*
(- /assistant: GenAI explanation) Tj
T*
(- /demo: simple browser-based demo UI) Tj
T*
(- /docs: Swagger API documentation) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
