T*
(MLflow model registry.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Grok / xAI API) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The GenAI assistant can call Grok using the xAI API when an API key is provided.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(The assistant is used for:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(- explaining predictions in business language) Tj
T*
(- summarizing why a product may be reordered) Tj
T*
(- making the output easier for business users to understand) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Environment variables:) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(  $env:XAI_API_KEY="your_key") Tj
T*
(  $env:XAI_MODEL="grok-4") Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(If no key is provided, the assistant uses a local fallback explanation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GitHub Actions) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(GitHub Actions is used for CI/CD validation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(It runs tests on push and pull request to ensure the codebase remains healthy.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Render) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Render is used to host the lightweight FastAPI demo.) Tj
T*
ET
